<subSubSection id="8CE1314C808B6575DAE7D1BF906FB70E" pageId="0" pageNumber="87" type="viviparous reproduction">
<paragraph id="82D0CB8D0608DACE6F961E0C3AE03801" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Viviparous reproduction.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DB6B9F286F230E7F6BD1319AA9595EDD" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">
One adult female (Holotype) was collected when pregnant, gave birth to eight neonates (including a couple of conjoined twins) on September 20th, 2017 in captivity. The weight of the normal neonates ranged between 3.00-3.45 g (3.01, 3.22, 3.22, 3.23, 3.28, 3.45, average = 3.235, 
<emphasis id="573F18EDB527A52AA3201CBC1FFE3D5A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">n</emphasis>
= 6). The weight of the conjoined twins was 2.86 g (weighed after the first shedding).
</paragraph>
